{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Encoding API","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API\">Encoding API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong>Encoding API</strong> provides a mechanism for handling text in various <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/character_encoding\">character encodings</a>, including legacy non-<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/UTF-8\">UTF-8</a> encodings.</p>\n<p>The API provides four interfaces: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code></a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code></a>.</p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfaces","title":"Interfaces","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/W